 "From the barracks, [to go] away, 20, 25 meters away, go away, to get away further, and, ah . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1801.473","u": "Tell me, Mr. Button, where are you, ah, where are your wife and children now?"},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1807.744","u": "My wife and my children are now in Paris, where I also am still, living in a Centre de [unintelligible] of the F&#195;d&#195;ration des Soci&#195;t&#195;s Juives de France."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1822.171","u": "You don&#39;t live in this house?"},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1823.890","u": "I live in this house."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1825.111","u": "And the wife and the children?"},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1826.619","u": "And my children, too, yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1828.232","u": "They, you live here, you have a room here?"},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1830.946","u": "Yes, I have a room here. I would like to . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1836.147","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1836.690","u": ". . . say something about the bad treatment of the Jews and other internees in Bergen-Belsen . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1845.027","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1845.344","u": ". . . and&#226;where I saw men and women who, in winter and in the snow and in, ah great cold, had large boards and carts to, ah . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1868.364","u": "Haul."},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1869.419","u": ". . . were stretched on carts on which one would normally only have, ah, horses, and, ah . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1881.447","u": "Mules . . ."},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1882.578","u": "Mu&#226;, Mules, ah . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1884.402","u": "Yoked . . ."},    {"who": "Jacob Button", "start": "1885.457","u": "Yo&#226;, yoked. Under very bad . . ."},    {"who": 