                                                                                                <b>Jacob Button</b>
                    <p class="utterance">. . . took it away. Such . . .</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">So, you stayed ashore with your wife and your kids?</p>
                                                                                                <b>Jacob Button</b>
                    <p class="utterance">I was, I stayed ashore with my wife and two children, two little children of six and eight years, and was to, afterwards, go back to Saloniki that was &#34;judenrein&#34; [free of Jews] as the Germans said.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
